       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI68208.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI68208.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Expense Reprt - Modificaçăo, Consulta, Eliminaçăo
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI68208         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD4805 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV6820.
       COPY COCV6821.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0010.
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.
       COPY ETCL0002.
       COPY ARCL7025.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT4805 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT4805'.
           05 CON-01       PIC X(02) VALUE '01'.
           05 CON-SEP      PIC X(01) VALUE '-'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME     PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI68208'.
           05 WS-DTMESANO          PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DTMESANO.
              10 WS-DTMESANO-ANO   PIC X(04).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-SEP1  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-MES   PIC X(02).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-SEP2  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-DIA   PIC X(02).
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI68208         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV6820-MSG.
           MOVE COCV6820-ASE               TO COCV6821-ASE.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV6820-ADE               TO COCV6821-ADE.

           PERFORM 2100-VALIDACOES
              THRU 2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-ELIMINA-DADOS
                 THRU 2299-ELIMINA-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-VALIDACOES.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDACOES' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Se despesa já aprovada năo pode apagar
      *    IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *    AND COCV6820-CAPROVADO NOT EQUAL SPACES
      *       MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
      *       MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV6821-CFUNCIONARIO-S
      *       MOVE COCK0001-JA-APROVADO-E TO COCV6821-CFUNCIONARIO-MSG
      *       MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC    TO COCV6821-CFUNCIONARIO-CAPLIC
      *    END-IF.


       2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-ELIMINA-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-ELIMINA-DADOS.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-ELIMINA-DADOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV6820-CFUNCIONARIO
             TO COCD4805-CIDEMP
           MOVE COCV6820-CEMPRESA
             TO COCD4805-CEMPRESA
           MOVE COCV6820-CANO
             TO WS-DTMESANO-ANO
           MOVE COCV6820-CMES
             TO WS-DTMESANO-MES
           MOVE CON-01
             TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
           MOVE CON-SEP
             TO WS-DTMESANO-SEP1
           MOVE CON-SEP
             TO WS-DTMESANO-SEP2
           MOVE WS-DTMESANO
             TO COCD4805-DTMESANO
           MOVE COCV6820-SEQ
             TO COCD4805-NSEQ


           EXEC SQL
                 DELETE FROM
                COVT4805_EXPENSE
                 WHERE CIDEMP       = :COCD4805-CIDEMP
                 AND   CEMPRESA     = :COCD4805-CEMPRESA
                 AND   DTMESANO     = :COCD4805-DTMESANO
                 AND   NSEQ         = :COCD4805-NSEQ
           END-EXEC


           MOVE CON-COVT4805               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO COCV6821-CFUNCIONARIO-S
                    MOVE COCK0001-CFUNCIONARIO-N-EXISTS
                      TO COCV6821-CFUNCIONARIO-MSG
                    MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                      TO COCV6821-CFUNCIONARIO-CAPLIC
              ELSE
                 IF NOT DB2-OK
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
           END-IF

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                        CONTINUE
           END-IF.

       2299-ELIMINA-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV6821-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV6821-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV6821-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0010.
           COPY VIAP0016.
           COPY ARCP7025.
